# Next.js App Router Rules

- **Routing**: App Router only. Pages and layouts live in `app/`.
- **Components**: Default to Server Components. Use `"use client"` only for hooks/interactivity. Default exports for pages and layouts.
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS for all styling. Avoid global CSS; CSS Modules only when Tailwind is insufficient.
- **Data fetching**: Server Actions for mutations; fetch in Server Components for reads. Use `@/lib/api` client — not raw `fetch` in components.
- **Naming**: `kebab-case` directories; `PascalCase` React components.
- **State**: Zustand for client state only — not raw DB records.
- **After changes**: `pnpm --filter web lint --fix && pnpm --filter web format && pnpm --filter web typecheck`
